{
  "stem": "16930.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 370.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wanted to get out-- her get-- get out of there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with the help of friends, of Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rosenfelder, who was running this-- this hostel-- hostel, she got her a job through a friend of hers-- as a-- she was trained as a secretary, a steno-typist then.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she got her a job, and she got her a place to live.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she was then able to move to London, which was very important for her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- because that was a bad place for her to be with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The father-- the man had died, and the woman was so possessive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so it was a bad place, it got to be a bad-- of course her life was saved, I mean.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it got to be a bad place to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We got her out, thank god, with the help of other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I couldn't have gotten her out myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I've had a good fortune in life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was always somebody there to help me, either give me a helping hand or to give me helping advice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Always throughout my life, I've had this good fortune.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and to this day, the people I can talk to about advice and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- so, when I got to-- so then I'm in America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I got here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I stayed with one of my uncles and aunts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went-- the second day was here, the following day was here, I went to the-- the unemployment office, for my card, for my social security card, and for a job.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they used to give-- there was plenty of jobs available, back in-- back in '54-- in the beginning of '54.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brooklyn, New York.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave me a job to a factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
